<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Coredns on All about Raspberry Pi</title><link>https://blog.hugozhu.site/tags/coredns/</link><description>Recent content in Coredns on All about Raspberry Pi</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.hugozhu.site/tags/coredns/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>用coredns做为主DNS解析内网的短域名</title><link>https://blog.hugozhu.site/post/2025/85-use-coredns-to-resolve-short-dns-name/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.hugozhu.site/post/2025/85-use-coredns-to-resolve-short-dns-name/</guid><description>&lt;p>在内网环境中，我们常常需要使用简单易记的短域名，而不是一些严格符合域名规范的全域名。通过CoreDNS，我们可以实现对短域名的自动解析，使内网运营更加高效和便捷。这篇文章将记录如何配置CoreDNS来支持这一功能。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>